dismissalText.commentary: Ajinkya Rahane c Rasikh Salam b Pandya 56 (31b 6x4 4x6 51m) SR: 180.64

dismissalComment.html: Pulled straight to deep-backward square leg, that's Rahane falling into the trap. Looked like he wanted to clear the boundary but couldn't generate enough power on the 98ks length ball on the pads. Shot was on, he went deep in the crease, and tried to lift it from down to up while on one knee. Just ended up finding the man. Two quick wickets for RCB
